,"tid":2368503,"uid":75597,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b8f3c0e3af3e1b0dbcaa4c1e1269460cbc13b394","tid":2368503,"uid":306591,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-18T04:44:36.000Z","msg":"我食必理痛冇用"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-18T04:47:54.000Z","msg":"食eve先得<br />\n食必理痛會想嘔"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-18T06:58:14.000Z","msg":"香港邊度買到eve呀？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-18T07:26:40.000Z","msg":"我都係幫襯代購咋<br />\n而家冇得去日本入貨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27e2f8fd4f3873b469c728d51cf5e210b23270b3","tid":2368503,"uid":22633,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-18T09:50:39.000Z","msg":"有冇人同我一樣，<br />\n四大止痛藥輪住食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n必理痛-&gt;樂信-&gt;幸福-&gt;克痛<br />\n<br />\n已經由每次1粒，進化到每次3粒先有效，<br />\n身邊人叫我每次試下忍住減啲，<br />\n唔好咁依賴止痛藥，<br />\n但係結果只有食左唔痛，同食左一樣咁撚痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有時臨訓食兩粒，屌凌晨4,5點痛醒，要食多3粒，<br />\n隔個幾鐘先再訓得著，<br />\n第二日全日冇精神<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後都係一開始食3粒冇咁嬲<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"237157285094c29cd3d2559d4860340f4fb70116","tid":2368503,"uid":22633,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"252e28eb80d2f233ed40b9508aa681dffd0b20f8","tid":2368503,"uid":75597,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b8f3c0e3af3e1b0dbcaa4c1e1269460cbc13b394","tid":2368503,"uid":306591,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cfb894565d53abc826e349bc2a890aaa66697f4e","tid":2368503,"uid":24368,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-16T10:23:57.000Z","msg":"上個月平均每星期要啪4粒必理痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-18T04:44:36.000Z","msg":"我食必理痛冇用"},"