ets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n冇原因下就會痛 好煩"},{"pid":"0a83fbf1e0b8fe67bfd343d1878f0683740a5f70","tid":2368503,"uid":237568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-18T12:01:08.000Z","msg":"我淨係夏天先偏頭痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c9404afb482c61c3a39738c492b0c45c98c044e","tid":2368503,"uid":234506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-18T12:04:37.000Z","msg":"我都係偏頭痛，有時係奶，有時係橙，有時朱古力。<br />\n一星期一兩次到，都係食Ibuprofen止痛"},{"pid":"e8278e5c400ce6fdc9843cdb73497b1bc0c70514","tid":2368503,"uid":380120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-18T14:21:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62d1247d8b59b4741f7caf68a2962461da0d3a8e","tid":2368503,"uid":297465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-18T16:05:32.000Z","msg":"我之前都成日偏頭頭,特別係訓得多/ 訓唔夠<br />\n<br />\n但之前跟個營養師搞番好啲飲食就冇了"},{"pid":"a285560e4cec202a98cdb44b4813e60cb6a1ee89","tid":2368503,"uid":37397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5d8eb67a8bbffb705c0c834edaaa1b8ff5bc018f","tid":2368503,"uid":22633,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"1dd2086544ba40b00fe7f1eeea5cafdb19466bfe","tid":2368503,"uid":37397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-17T06:28:11.000Z","msg":"有冇試過呼吸法？"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-17T15:06:14.000Z","msg":"咩黎架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n講到鬼滅咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-18T17:52:57.000Z","msg":"冇聽過調息?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65f5a3b7472555a41b4547fbd6b145be80ebb17f","tid":2368503,"uid":142003,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-18T18:19:53.000Z","msg":"正視聽+腦內科keep 住覆診中既講下<br />\n偏頭痛係搏動性，你會feel 到三叉神經位，血管跟住脈搏每跳一下就痛一下<br />\n普通頭痛係keep 住痛一段時間，痛到你有時都唔記得左痛緊<br />\n&quot;&quot;分別在好似插左把刀落去唔郁，同插把刀蚊出黎再插落去咁loop&quot;&quot;<br />\n<br />\n多數醫生初期都係比降血壓藥......男仔食太耐會容易the......<br />\n真正止到偏頭痛既藥物多數都係貴，我由$80一粒食到無咩效果，依家食緊個隻$100一粒<br />\n<br />\n真偏頭痛會痛到有閃光有全身標汗暈嘔搭黨鐵都嘔企唔定，發作原因因人而異<br />\n有時我未訓醒係個夢入面已經話緊比自己聽好頭痛快d 起身食藥，一睜開眼個刻只有心底一句fuck my life<br />\n<br />\n除非照到真係有腫瘤/血管畸生，唔係既就好似我咁袋定急救藥，只不過食左唔等於閃光頭暈嘔既問題會消失，只係止左痛"},{"pid":"561af0bb5bfef482b1dd83c41e1dde403d93c4a8","tid":2368503,"uid":264719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-18T20:20:07.000Z","msg":"有冇試過食CBD 聽人講可以止埋痛"},{"pid":"19f141e276bfa50383975443f7abee64503e71b0","tid":2368503,"uid":47374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-18T20:23:53.000Z","msg":"前兩日痛到閪"},{"pid":"c50e5e862b83b038ae4ec8c00638d4cb71266ffb","tid":2368503,"uid":177924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T22:44:43.000Z","msg":"痛左6 7年<br />\n自從食左鋅片之後好左好撚多"},{"pid":"71f3ebfc603360adb103c12035f11734d8c9d0fd","tid":2368503,"uid":249923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c50e5e862b83b038ae4ec8c00638d4cb71266ffb","tid":2368503,"uid":177924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T22:44:43.000Z","msg":"痛左6 7年<br />\n自從食左鋅片之後好左好撚多"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-10T02:21:56.000Z","msg":"真架？ 係咪一日食一次？ 有冇話劑量要幾多？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e25cd270b25eb77d3bfd379bc357926ee19ee40e","tid":2368503,"uid":177924,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"71f3ebfc603360adb103c12035f11734d8c9d0fd","tid":2368503,"uid":249923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c50e5e862b83b038ae4ec8c00638